title: Vocal Trance Work Out Hits 2014 (320kbps) (AciDToX8)

Vocal Trance Work Out Hits 2014 

                  Trance, Vocal, Uplifting | Amsterdam Trance

              320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 03:36:53 | 502 Mb


Motivation is the key to keeping you primed in the gym, running the extra mile, pushing heavier weight and taking your achievements one step further. And what better motivator is there than Trance music? We asked the experts - our dedicated Fitness fans - what music makes their heart rate rise and gets them pumped to hit new heights and here are our Top 30 workout Choons. This compilation includes music from Armin van Buuren, Richard Durand, Above & Beyond, John O'Callaghan, Rafael Frost, Beat Service, Ana Criado, Omnia, Nitrous Oxide & Susana among the many..
